I just watched this film and it was very surprising to me, as I always say if they find the right Actress, or Actor, to pull off believable real-life situations then they'd have a pretty good movie. And it worked! at least for this one , so far. I but I like the whole series , in wich  I have all 3 Movies. The developing Actresses in the film were pretty good, as for some of them being their first film. The 4 girls jelled together really well. this made the film even more realistic. Now I have some news for those who have been asking me ,that I just found out the Clint Black is rumored to be producing Flicka 4, and I believe this be true, because they asked him in Flicka 3, if he'd come back for the 4th installment, he said "yes"
So there you have it!  You have watch the special features in Flicka 3 to see it.
